### AYYUAZ.APP API Test Endpoints

@host = https://localhost:7000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Detailed Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/detailed

###
### Authentication Tests
###

### Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "confirmPassword": "password123"
}

### Admin Login (Seeded Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "Admin045@gmail.com",
    "password": "admin123"
}

### Get Current User Info (requires Bearer token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###
### Category Tests
###

### Get All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/category

### Get Category by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/category/1

### Create Category (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/category
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Name"

Test Category
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Description"

This is a test category created via API
--WebAppBoundary--

### Search Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/category/search?searchTerm=Electronics

### Get Categories with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/category/paged?page=1&pageSize=5

###
### Product Tests
###

### Get All Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/product

### Get Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/1

### Get Products by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/category/1

### Search Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/search?searchTerm=Wireless

### Get Products by Price Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/price-range?minPrice=20&maxPrice=50

### Get Available Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/available

### Get Latest Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/latest?count=5

### Get Featured Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/featured

### Get Products with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/product/paged?page=1&pageSize=5

### Create Product (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/product
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Name"

Test Product
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Description"

This is a test product created via API
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Price"

29.99
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Stock"

10
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="CategoryId"

1
--WebAppBoundary--

###
### Order Tests
###

### Create Order (Public)
POST {{baseUrl}}/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "fullName": "John Doe",
    "phoneNumber": "+1234567890",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "address": "123 Main St, City, State 12345",
    "notes": "Please deliver after 6 PM",
    "orderItems": [
        {
            "productId": 1,
            "quantity": 2,
            "unitPrice": 99.99
        },
        {
            "productId": 2,
            "quantity": 1,
            "unitPrice": 19.99
        }
    ]
}

### Get All Orders (Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Recent Orders (Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/recent?count=5
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Orders with Pagination (Admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/paged?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

