### Settings Tests
###

### Get All Settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings

### Get Current Settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/current

### Get Contact Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/contact/phone

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/contact/email

###
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/contact/address

### Get Social Media Links
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/social-media

### Update Settings (Admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/settings/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "AYYUAZ Store Updated",
    "phoneNumber": "+1-234-567-8901",
    "address": "456 Updated Street, New City, NC 54321",
    "email": "updated@ayyuazstore.com",
    "facebookUrl": "https://facebook.com/ayyuazstore",
    "instagramUrl": "https://instagram.com/ayyuazstore",
    "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/ayyuazstore"
}

