POST {{baseUrl}}/settings/backup
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Check Username Uniqueness
GET {{baseUrl}}/category/check-name?name=NewCategory

### Check Email Uniqueness
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/check-email?email=test@example.com